{"tid":1454614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加大力度對旅客/國際宣傳popo安排內鬼於示威者中","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:34.000Z","uid":53349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2976b42aa5c2c54981eca266a53dfabc4f3dc07b","tid":1454614,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:57:49.000Z","msg":"國際舞台就算對方黎講，都係一個好好嘅地方，可以向國際污名化我哋，最壞情況係屈我哋恐襲。<br />\n今日出埋旗手，絕對係裡應外合污名化後暴力清場。<br />\n而我哋就對外宣佈由衝擊都係暴力清場都係popo嘅劇本。衝擊唔一定係衝禁區，可以係攻擊旅客，甚至破壞設施同時破壞我哋嘅形象。<br />\n<br />\n補充：我哋嘅目的係癱瘓機場，咁塞爆已經夠做，noise都好大，唔需要再作任何衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc649b13753fefee6efa2a35878875c56dfc1f98","tid":1454614,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加強</span></span></strong><br />\n唔撚係加大力度"},{"pid":"467d359072f295eea24c3938002cda98cfb0f46d","tid":1454614,"uid":53349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fc649b13753fefee6efa2a35878875c56dfc1f98","tid":1454614,"uid":299171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加強</span></span></strong><br />\n唔撚係加大力度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"sor, 心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加強加強加強加強加強加強加強加強加強加強 罰抄十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e8d6ab88f4ce4eeb21f9a3c4597f55babe701d","tid":1454614,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}